Game information:

Worms Revolution is the latest game in the classic turn-based strategy
series to come to the PC, featuring exciting new features and beautiful
3D graphics whilst retaining the classic 2D gameplay that fans love

Choose to play the extensive single player mode which features both
campaign and puzzle missions or dive straight into multiplayer warfare via
online or local play. For the first time ever see the inclusion of dynamic
water, physics objects and worm classes! Customize your experience by
choosing what classes you play with, what they look like and even how they
speak!

Worms Revolution sticks an exploding sheep under worm-on-worm conflict and
blasts it squarely into the 21st century

